<div><head>《五經析疑》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.2">漢制：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.3">先冬至三日晝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.4">冬至後三日晝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.5">漏四十五刻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.6">夜五十五刻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.7">先夏至三日晝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.8">夏至後三日晝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.9">漏六十五刻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-1a.10">夜三十五刻。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.2">先王之制禮樂也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.3">制禮以節事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.4">修樂以導志，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.5">故觀其禮樂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.6">理亂自知也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.7">聞角聲無不側隱而慈者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-2a.8">聞商聲無不斷割而亡事者。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.2">夫笙者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.3">法萬物始生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.4">導達陰陽之氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.5">故有長短，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.6">黃鐘之始，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.7">象法鳳凰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.8">竝《初學記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.9">矢絕於弦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.10">不可追止；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.11">執戟在手，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.12">制之在人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-3a.13">《御覽》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.2">甲女子道逢暴風飛沙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.3">發屋惶怖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.4">走，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.5">欲趨乙門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.6">凶凶懼欲閉門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.7">甲女求欲入門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.8">為乙門所笇死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.9">乙何罪？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.10">吏議以為當坐殺人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.11">當棄市也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1189_CHANT_001-4a.12">《書鈔》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
